ira Shinomiya(Ozin Osbourne)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mdpr.jp/news/detail/1399960|script-title=ja:仲里依紗ら追加出演者発表「a-nation」×「GirlsAward」ファッションショー|date=2014-08-06|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref>}} | August 14–20, 2014 |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mdpr.jp/anation2014/|script-title=ja:a-nation island & stadium fes. 2014 powered by ウイダーinゼリー|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref> |- |align="center"| - | A-Nation&GirlsAward island collection in [[Taiwan]] | September 13, 2014 |<ref name="oricon20140913"/> |- |align="center"| - | A-Nation&GirlsAward island collection in [[Singapore]] | October 18, 2014 |<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mdpr.jp/news/detail/1438261|script-title=ja:藤井リナ、八木アリサ、石田ニコルら「a-nation」シンガポールで大歓声|date=2014-10-19|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref> |- |align="center"| 10 | [[GirlsAward 2014 Autumn/Winter]] | {{dts|2014|10|01}} |<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mdpr.jp/news/detail/1413968|script-title=ja:西内まりや「GirlsAward」でライブパフォーマンス 豪華出演者も追加発表|date=2014-09-05|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref> |- |align="center"| 11 | [[GirlsAward 2015 Spring/Summer]] | {{dts|2015|04|29}} |<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mdpr.jp/music/detail/1466526|script-title=ja:AKB48＆乃木坂46が競演 豪華出演者発表＜GirlsAward 2015 S/S＞|date=2015-02-10|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref> |- |align="center"| 12 | [[GirlsAward 2015 Autumn/Winter]] | {{dts|2015|10|24}} |<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mdpr.jp/news/detail/1536469|script-title=ja:北川景子がトップバッター クールな流し目で圧巻オーラ＜GirlsAward 2015 A/W＞|date=2015-10-24|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref> |- |align="center"| 13 | [[GirlsAward 2016 Spring/Summer]] | {{dts|2016|04|09}} |<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mdpr.jp/news/detail/1577078|script-title=ja:武井咲、トップバッターで「ガルアワ」開幕 美脚あらわなミニショーパン姿に歓声＜GirlsAward 2016 S/S＞|accessdate=2016-10-24|publisher=modelpress|language=Japanese}}</ref> |- |align="